<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    
    <% include ../partials/head %>
  <body>

    <% include ../partials/header %>


    <div class="container pt-2">
      <% include ../partials/alerts %>
      <div class='row'>
        <div class="offset2 col-md-12">
          <h1>OpenTrade affiliate program</h1>
          <p>Your affiliate program is enabled, and you can earn commissions by adding your affiliate tag ?ref=<span id='refid'><%- status.id || 0 %></span> to any OpenTrade URL</p>
          <p>Affiliation is registered when any user activates new account from a flyer generated from your affiliate account.</p>
          <h2>Example links:</h2>
          <pre>
            https://trade.multicoins.org/?ref=<span id='refid'><%- status.id || 0 %></span>
            https://trade.multicoins.org/market/MC-BTC?ref=<span id='refid'><%- status.id || 0 %></span>
          </pre>
          <h2>Statistics</h2>
          <p>You are currently registered as an affiliate for <strong id='usersAll'>0</strong> users and will earn commissions from all <span class='text-danger'>BUY orders</span> done by these. Total <strong id='allVisits'></strong> visits have been done through your links.</p>
          <hr>
          Please note: <strong>You have got payments <span class='text-danger'>only</span> from <span class='text-danger'>BUY</span> orders !</strong>
          <hr>
          <h2>Latest payouts</h2>
          <table class='table'>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Time</th>
                <th>Amount</th>
                <th>Comment</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody id='table_payouts'>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <h2>Latest converted users</h2>
          <table class='table'>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Date converted</th>
                <th>Trade volume</th>
                <th>Landing page</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody id='table_referals'>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          
        </div>
      </div>

    </div> <!-- /container -->


    <% include ../partials/footer %>
    <script src='/js/referals.js'></script>
  </body>
</html>
